Ukrainian steelmaker Donetskstal
Metallurgical Plant CJSC will close its open hearth furnace with
a 660,000 tons of steel a year capacity from April,
 Ekonomicheskie Izvestia  newspaper reported, without citing
anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
